              "code": "3\n4\n1 2 -1\n-3 0 -3\n-1 4 -5\n1 2 -4\n5\n3 0 0\n1 0 -5\n-3 0 0\n-1 0 10\n1 0 -10\n5\n884 -667 497\n680 -973 213\n23 -548 -412\n826 359 -333\n773 212 218",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "输出",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
